  "description": "<p>有时候非常简单的表情能够传达文字之外的更多情感，也让表达的内容变得更加生动。在经过最近几年发展，表情已经发生了翻天覆地的变化，从简单的文字符号组合（比如=) -_- T_T =P ;)）变成各种动态渲染，<strong>那么你知道最早使用表情是什么时候吗？根据记载最早使用表情的是1981年3月30日出版的《Puck》杂志，在排版艺术中间页上使用了笑脸，忧郁和冷漠等表情。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec47eb2/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245029.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%91%E8%84%B8%E7%AD%89%E8%A1%A8%E6%83%85%E7%AC%A6%E5%8F%B7%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E5%88%B01981%E5%B9%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245029.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%91%E8%84%B8%E7%AD%89%E8%A1%A8%E6%83%85%E7%AC%A6%E5%8F%B7%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E5%88%B01981%E5%B9%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245029.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%91%E8%84%B8%E7%AD%89%E8%A1%A8%E6%83%85%E7%AC%A6%E5%8F%B7%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E5%88%B01981%E5%B9%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245029.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%91%E8%84%B8%E7%AD%89%E8%A1%A8%E6%83%85%E7%AC%A6%E5%8F%B7%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E5%88%B01981%E5%B9%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=h